                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 823.00/147.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">McMillin</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Lima</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-03-27">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 27, 1914</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Conferences ineffectual in reaching final agreement. Decree again convening
                    Congress in extra session May 15 issued five o’clock this morning.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">McMillin</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
